      <title>菲律宾副总统杜特尔特准备为弹劾辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-vp-duterte-preparing-defense-against-impeachment-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾副总统萨拉·杜特尔特周三表示，她正在准备对针对她的弹劾指控进行辩护，但她对能否获得立法者足够的支持来对抗弹劾表示怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-vp-duterte-preparing-defense-against-impeachment-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 06:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋敲定协议以促进与俄罗斯等国的贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/uae-finalizes-pact-to-boost-trade-with-nations-including-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿联酋与欧亚经济联盟达成经济协议，旨在通过降低关税和消除贸易壁垒来增加非石油双边贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/uae-finalizes-pact-to-boost-trade-with-nations-including-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨将请求信任投票，引发 2 月选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/scholz-to-request-confidence-vote-triggering-february-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨将于周三向德国议会下院提交一份请愿书，正式请求在 12 月 16 日举行信任投票，以引发 2 月底的提前选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/scholz-to-request-confidence-vote-triggering-february-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜首次就危机发表评论 抨击尹富强“独裁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/north-korea-slams-yoon-dictatorship-in-first-comment-on-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，朝鲜首次对韩国政治局势发表评论，谴责韩国总统尹锡烈试图实施戒严。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/north-korea-slams-yoon-dictatorship-in-first-comment-on-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 04:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
